	ADDMISCBUTTON("Mass Immune Apoth", "MassImmuneApothCommand", TRUE, -1, 0, -1, "Uses 10s immune apoth on all chars. A little slower than Mass Absolute Domain because" & @CRLF & "bot has to locate where in inventory the Immune apoth is. Still very strong though in a pinch.")
