	ADDMISCBUTTON("Mass Nuke", "MassNukeNoGenieChi", TRUE, -1, 0, -1, "Standard mass nuke that starts with characters triple sparking." & @CRLF & "Characters then start casting Macro(3) on selected target." & @CRLF & "Continues until you move your character. Alts will follow you (if setting permits) when you move the main character. Selecting different targets continues the nuke" & @CRLF & @CRLF & "Strongest sin uses life hunter spam if your setting permits it" & @CRLF & @CRLF & "NEW: All classes set gearset #1 to Attack gear. Seekers set gearset #3 to DEF LVL gear." & @CRLF & 'See "Mass Nuke Settings" under Info > Settings for more customizations.')
